Lib::Sonypi
===========

DESCRIPTION

This is a Perl interface to sonypi Linux kernel module.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Perl v5.6.1

sonypi related software may be obtained from http://www.popies.net/sonypi/
And also from: http://www.linux.it/~malattia/wiki/index.php/Sony_drivers

